# Normalise text in the repo, but pin the Windows launchers to CRLF on checkout.
# เปิดระบบ.bat is parsed by cmd.exe by byte offset (see docs/adr/0006), so its
# line endings must not vary by whoever clones it.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.bat text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

*.png binary
*.db binary
*.xlsx binary
